@* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * LAYOUT AÇIKLAMASI - _LayoutDashboard.cshtml
 * ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * 
 * [AMAÇ]
 * Admin ve User panel sayfaları için ana layout.
 * Modern, responsive, glassmorphism tasarım dili.
 * 
 * [ÖZELLİKLER]
 * - Sidebar navigation (Responsive - Mobile'da slide-in)
 * - Dark mode desteği (LocalStorage persistence)
 * - User profile card
 * - Role-based navigation (Admin/User)
 * - TempData ile otomatik AlertService entegrasyonu
 * - Smooth animations ve transitions
